02:05.959 --> 02:08.253
Pass me some paper towels, please.

02:10.422 --> 02:12.883
- Well, what about our
big donor Stan what's-his-name?

02:12.883 --> 02:14.176
MINISTER PAYNE:
No, I don't want that prick's money.

02:14.176 --> 02:15.594
