02:34.947 --> 02:37.407
Suck it up and learn
how to fuckin' tap dance.

02:41.119 --> 02:42.162
- Happy?

02:44.581 --> 02:47.417
MAGGIE:
What about this one? It's got a balcony.

02:47.417 --> 02:49.461
