and I felt much better.

03:45.392 --> 03:48.061
And then I thought,
"You know what else doesn't feel right?"

03:48.061 --> 03:49.730
What my lawyer is saying.

03:50.397 --> 03:51.940
So I told him.

03:51.940 --> 03:55.068
"No. I belong in jail."

03:55.068 --> 03:59.072
