05:13.814 --> 05:16.400
LUIS:
Hey, but what do I put for special skills?

05:16.400 --> 05:17.484
- What can you do?

05:17.484 --> 05:20.988
[beatboxing]

05:24.324 --> 05:25.409
- Yeah.

05:26.994 --> 05:28.912
- Just put Microsoft Word.

05:28.912 --> 05:30.122
- Minister Payne.

05:30.122 --> 05:31.832
You know those billionaires
I was telling you about?

05:31.832 --> 05:34.334
They wanna come by and get a tour
and see what we're all about.

05:34.334 --> 05:36.795
LUIS:
Oh, hell, yeah, my boy!

05:36.795 --> 05:39.173
I never met billionaires before.

05:39.173 --> 05:40.799
I got a lot of questions for those fools.

05:40.799 --> 05:43.218
- Those fuckers are only coming
for the photo op.

05:43.218 --> 05:45.804
They'll leave giving us
nothing more than pennies.

05:45.804 --> 05:48.682
I'd rather focus
on increasing cupcake sales

05:48.682 --> 05:51.268
or win a fucking scratch-off
for once in my life.

05:51.268 --> 05:53.270
- Payne, stop being a little bitch.

05:53.270 --> 05:54.813
Look, I'll do all the work.

05:54.813 --> 05:57.441
All you have to do is
show up, smile, and look pretty.

05:58.984 --> 06:01.236
- Fine. I'll fuckin' do it.

06:01.236 --> 06:03.697
- So let's get you
some new clothes, and an iron.

06:04.239 --> 06:05.782
- It's good if I look like shit.

06:05.782 --> 06:07.618
