06:07.618 --> 06:08.785
JULIO:
Yeah, but not that bad.

06:08.785 --> 06:10.871
Crease your fuckin' pants, playboy.

06:10.871 --> 06:12.080
You look like a fuckin' bum.

06:12.080 --> 06:14.708
- I am a fuckin' bum. I live in a van.

06:14.708 --> 06:16.084
