♪ Billionaires ♪

06:16.084 --> 06:18.712
♪ Gonna give my, buh-huh,
résumé to billionaires ♪

06:18.712 --> 06:21.048
- You will not fuckin' beatbox
for those billionaires.

06:21.048 --> 06:23.175
