07:05.008 --> 07:06.134
- Oh, shit, ghetto bird!

07:06.134 --> 07:07.761
[whirring continues]

07:08.846 --> 07:12.474
- Alright, everyone, the future
of Hugs Not Thugs depends on today.

07:12.474 --> 07:16.645
So act reformed, but we need their money,
