07:45.549 --> 07:47.301
- Aw. Well, thank you for having us.

07:47.301 --> 07:49.219
I mean, we are just so happy to be here.

07:49.720 --> 07:51.430
- Yeah, I've had a small taste

07:51.430 --> 07:52.931
of what everyone here has been through.

07:52.931 --> 07:55.392
