07:56.977 --> 07:59.938
JULIO: Whoa!
- Dominic, no, no need for that today.

07:59.938 --> 08:02.649
That's okay. They're reformed.
Harmless now.

08:02.649 --> 08:06.069
- Hello. I'm Luis Hernandez,
future entrepreneur.

08:06.069 --> 08:07.487
- Well, alright!
LUIS: Nice to meet you.

08:08.697 --> 08:11.909
- Luis is a shining example
of our program.

08:11.909 --> 08:13.243
LUIS:
Hey, but on the real though,

08:13.243 --> 08:15.329
how'd you guys come up on all that money?

08:15.329 --> 08:17.623
[Julio laughs nervously]

08:17.623 --> 08:20.000
- Luis, our resident joker.

08:20.000 --> 08:21.293
RICHARD:
It's okay. I don't mind him asking.

08:21.293 --> 08:24.087
