08:24.963 --> 08:27.049
- Damn. That's smart.

08:27.049 --> 08:30.177
- Let me introduce you
to our fearless leader,

08:30.177 --> 08:32.346
Minister Leonard Payne.

08:32.346 --> 08:34.848
He really gives everything
he has to the program.

08:34.848 --> 08:37.935
No matter how frustrating
a situation might be,

08:37.935 --> 08:40.812
he selflessly does
what he's supposed to do

08:40.812 --> 08:42.397
for the greater good.

08:43.190 --> 08:44.191
Always.

08:45.692 --> 08:46.860
- Nice to meet you both.

08:46.860 --> 08:49.279
- Oh, come here.
- Oh, nice to meet you. What?

08:49.279 --> 08:51.573
