RHONDA: Hmm.

08:51.573 --> 08:53.659
- We read all about you
on the helicopter ride over.

08:53.659 --> 08:56.161
- An angel in human form.
That's what we're looking at.

08:56.161 --> 08:57.162
RICHARD:
Mm-hmm.

08:57.162 --> 08:58.956
