09:08.715 --> 09:10.717
We make do with what we have.

09:10.717 --> 09:14.346
But the truth is, we have more applicants
than we can service at this facility.

09:14.346 --> 09:17.850
And as you can see,
we're sorely in need of new technology.

09:17.850 --> 09:21.311
- Damn, these outdated computers
just won't load.

09:22.312 --> 09:24.439
