[Julio mouths]

09:24.439 --> 09:25.482
[keyboard keys clacking]

09:32.573 --> 09:34.366
- If only I had a new job,

09:35.158 --> 09:36.994
I would be able to get a computer

09:36.994 --> 09:38.996
and then I would get a new job.

09:38.996 --> 09:41.039
And I would never go back to prison.

09:41.039 --> 09:42.958
Before Hugs Not Thugs,

09:43.542 --> 09:45.460
