by our huggers in their art therapy class.

10:25.042 --> 10:26.627
- Absolutely amazing work.

10:26.627 --> 10:30.130
RHONDA: Oh, my God.
I love this one of the crying peasant.

10:30.130 --> 10:31.590
- That one's cool, I guess.

10:31.590 --> 10:32.758
